snippet.title: King of Seas - Release Date Trailer May25th
snippet.description:
Ahoy, me Hearties! We are thrilled to announce that King of Seas, will be launching from a port near you on 25th May 2021! This action-packed seafaring adventure will be available for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, PC and Nintendo Switch.

That’s not all! Starting today a brand new demo for King of Seas (PC) will be available via the Steam page. Don't forget to add the game to your wishlist!

King of Seas on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1209410/King_of_Seas/
